1) Requirement libraries
   libmicrohttdpd for server
   libcurl for client
  $ sudo apt-get install curl libc6 libcurl3 zlib1g

2) Installation
  2-1) For client only
   $ make watch_and_transfer
   or
   $ make watch_and_transfer2
  2-2) For client and server
   $ make

3) How to use watch_and_transfer
  
